Reliance Power Taking 70 Billion Rupee Samalkot Loan, Times Says

-- B y   K a r t i k a y   M e h r o t r a
-- 
2011-03-24T03:39:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/reliance-power-taking-70-billion-rupee-samalkot-loan-times-says.html
Reliance Power Ltd. (RPWR)  is in an
advanced stage of borrowing 70 billion rupees ($1.56 billion)
for its 2,400 megawatt gas-based plant at Samalkot, the Economic
Times reported, citing unidentified people.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Chacko at 
 jchacko@bloomberg.net  